This function is accomplished through a form of event , Can form in a node , Form event production seen . 2, According to the reimbursement amount , Set the direction of the condition , You can right-click on the connection line , See conditions set direction steering . 3, This process uses a waterfall approach design , So there are two 【 Financial reimbursement 】 Node , But you can see , Different paths flow movement , So different forms . 4, On each node , Use a picture signature . Special note here : Picture signature is not equal to the electronic signature . 5, This process design used in all forms of free form , If you want to see the effect fool form , Please form type node property is set .
